FBIS4-41275 "drsov121_f_94001" FBIS-SOV-94-121 Daily Report 22 Jun 1994 National Affairs Kravchuk Vetoes Local Election Law Kravchuk Vetoes Local Election Law LD2206190794 Kiev Radio Ukraine World Service in Ukrainian 1800 GMT 22 Jun 94 LD2206190794 Kiev Radio Ukraine World Service Ukrainian BFN [Text] Ukrainian President Leonid Kravchuk has used his constitutional right of veto against the law on the formation of local bodies of power and self-government which was recently passed by the Supreme Council of Ukraine. The president has referred the law to the parliament for amendment. He announced this on Wednesday during a meeting with ministers and heads of departments on security issues. According to Leonid Kravchuk, some articles of the law contradict the constitution and the current legislation.
